name: R2 Fire Resistant
Group_Name: West Chester R2 Fire Resistant
meta_title: R2 Fire Resistant
meta_description: West Chester 86716S R2 Fire Resistant
small_image_label: R2 Fire Resistant
thumbnail_label: R2 Fire Resistant
description: West Chester 86716S R2 Fire Resistant
short_description:
R2 Fire Resistant glove features flame retardant Kevlar® knit fabric on back of hand and knitwrist cuff to protect workers in the event of flash fires. Dual layer goatskin leather palm combines flame resistant properties with the toughness of leather. Kevlar® reinforced thumb saddle and TPR knuckle, finger, and back of hand protection provide extra protection against bumps and pinches.
  • Digital printing on top layer of goatskin leather provides traction and grip
  • Zero predicted burn injury tested in accordance with ASTM F1930 and meets ASTM 6413 for flame resistance
  • Added TPR protection on impact zones

name: Rugged Rigger Orange Glove
Group_Name: West Chester Rugged Rigger Orange Glove
meta_title: Rugged Rigger Orange Glove
meta_description: West Chester 86710S Rugged Rigger Orange Glove
small_image_label: Rugged Rigger Orange Glove
thumbnail_label: Rugged Rigger Orange Glove
description: West Chester 86710S Rugged Rigger Orange Glove
short_description:
Rugged Rigger™ has 4 way stretch spandex in back of hand, Parity™ synthetic leather palm with Clarino™palm and finger patches, TPR knuckle, finger and back of hand protection, Kevlar® reinforced thumb saddle, Parity™ synthetic forchettes, oil resistant padding.
  • TPR finger, hand and knuckle guards to protect against bumps & bruises
  • Reinforced thermoplastic fingertips to reduce pinches; Kevlar reinforced thumb saddle
  • Flexible 4-way stretch form fitting spandex back with Hi Visibility fabric and oil resistant palm providing excellent grip in wet applications
  • ANSI 1, 273 gms

name: R2 Safety Cut with Long Neoprene Cuff - Orange
Group_Name: West Chester R2 Safety Cut with Long Neoprene Cuff - Orange
meta_title: R2 Safety Cut with Long Neoprene Cuff - Orange
meta_description: West Chester 86715S R2 Safety Cut with Long Neoprene Cuff - Orange
small_image_label: R2 Safety Cut with Long Neoprene Cuff - Orange
thumbnail_label: R2 Safety Cut with Long Neoprene Cuff - Orange
description: West Chester 86715S R2 Safety Cut with Long Neoprene Cuff - Orange
short_description:
R2 Safety Cut features a cut-resistant knit Kevlar™ lined palm while the pique lining w/CoolPass on the back of hand wicks away sweat. Built in Enprotex liner provides a waterproof barrier to keep moisture out. Glove palm and fingers feature synthetic leather overlayed with additional layer of synthetic leather printed with red silicone pattern for an oil resistant, better visibility grip. Back of hand impact zones protect against bumps and bruises.
  • TPR finger, fingertips, hand and knuckle guards to protect against bumps & bruises
  • Kevlar™ lined palm and extended Kevlar™ reinforced thumb saddle protects against cuts and slashes
  • Flexible 4-way Hi Visibility stretch spandex back lined with moisture-wicking pique with CoolPass, Enprotex® waterproof barrier, and oil resistant palm providing excellent grip in wet applications
  • ANSI 3, 1190 g

name: 35ml 2pc PVC Hydroblast Rainsuit
Group_Name: West Chester 35ml 2pc PVC Hydroblast Rainsuit
meta_title: 35ml 2pc PVC Hydroblast Rainsuit
meta_description: West Chester 4040M 35ml 2pc PVC Hydroblast Rainsuit
small_image_label: 35ml 2pc PVC Hydroblast Rainsuit
thumbnail_label: 35ml 2pc PVC Hydroblast Rainsuit
description: West Chester 4040M 35ml 2pc PVC Hydroblast Rainsuit
short_description:
This 2 piece splash suit is specifically designed to keep water out. The rainsuit is constructed with .35ml PVC on polyester with hook and loop closures on all openings to provide a watertight seal.
  • Jacket has an attached hood with hook and loop chin strap. Four-snap front closure with hook and loop storm flap, open wrists with adjustable hook and loop closures with a drawstring at the waist.
  • Overalls have open ankles with adjustable hook and loop closures. Adjustable elastic suspenders with center thumb cam buckles. Side snaps for sizing.
  • Snap-on neck guard for added protection.

name: Heavy Duty 40ml 2pc Acid Suit
Group_Name: West Chester Heavy Duty 40ml 2pc Acid Suit
meta_title: Heavy Duty 40ml 2pc Acid Suit
meta_description: West Chester 4045M Heavy Duty 40ml 2pc Acid Suit
small_image_label: Heavy Duty 40ml 2pc Acid Suit
thumbnail_label: Heavy Duty 40ml 2pc Acid Suit
description: West Chester 4045M Heavy Duty 40ml 2pc Acid Suit
short_description:
This 2 piece acid suit is ideal for heavy applications. 40ml PVC/polyester/PVC construction is ASTM D 6413 certified for chemical resistance and flame resistance.
  • Jacket has an attached drawstring hood for secure fit. Vented cape back and underarm vents for a wide range of motion and comfort. Four snap front closure. Open wrist with adjustable snap closures.
  • Overalls have open ankles with adjustable snap closures. Adjustable suspenders with triangular D-ring buckles and studs. Snap to fit sizing at the waist for a secure fit.
  • Two flap pockets to secure valuables.

description: West Chester 835012 Black PVC Steel Toe Boot
short_description:
Reinforced Steel Toe and Steel shank from arch to heel, this heavy duty 16" Black PVC Boot provides excellent barrier protection from liquids and chemicals. Known as "Cement" boot are worn over the sock.
  • Steel Toe and Steel Shank for extra protection from fallen items.

  • Kick off Lug. Yellow dot on toe indicate steel reinforce toe and shank. Removable insole. Unlined with storage bag.
  • Passes ASTM F 2412-05 & ASTM F 2413-05 for Impact Resistance and Compression Resistance
